                            <comment id="13988827" author="lefty@hortonworks.com" created="Sat, 3 May 2014 22:20:51 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;This bug seems like a good thing to document in the wiki for releases 0.12.0 through 0.13.1, especially considering how cryptic the error message is.  Does it also apply to release 0.11.0 without the -f option?  (In other words, can a query provided with the -e option have multiple lines?)&lt;/p&gt;

